snippet: The Jamaican sprinter Yohan Blake experienced a setback in his return from injury, pulling up during the 100 meters at the Glasgow Grand Prix, falling to the track and leaving in a wheelchair.
abstract: Jamaican sprinter Yohan Blake suffers setback in his return from injury, pulling up during 100 meters at the Glasgow Grand Prix, falling to track and leaving in wheelchair; other track and field news noted.
